data.description:
Large corner lot with new fence in the back yard. Open floor plan with kitchen open to the living area. Tall ceilings at the entrance and in the living area give a spacious feel.

Built ins in the kitchen and living room. Formal dining room and office just inside the front door. 

Large bonus room could be used as game or multi-media room.

Expandable room just of the bonus room.

Close to Snowden Grove and Silo Square. Minutes from all types of shopping needs. 

Water feature, gazebo, and fire pit in the back yard. Plenty of space to entertain.

Leaf Guard installed in gutters. Wifi capabilities throughout the home for a variety of systems and applications for operation will be provided.
